// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0428 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 854e3bc9-1213-5f40-aa84-631a841eff84

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:2* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:7* OR ImageFileName = *photon os:2.0* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
